  "prompt": "What do you do on rainy days?",
  "response": "On rainy days, people often choose to stay indoors and engage in activities that they enjoy. Here are a few common things people might do:\n\n1. **Read a book**: Cozying up with a good book can be a great way to pass the time.\n2. **Watch movies or binge-watch TV shows**: Rainy days are perfect for catching up on films or series.\n3. **Cook or bake**: Trying out new recipes or baking treats can be enjoyable and rewarding.\n4. **Craft or do DIY projects**: Engaging in creative hobbies or home improvement tasks can keep you entertained.\n5. **Play games**: Board games or video games can provide fun challenges for solo or group play.\n6. **Listen to music or podcasts**: It's a great time to discover new tunes or learn something new through interesting podcasts.\n7. **Relax and pamper yourself**: Taking time for a spa day at home or practicing mindfulness can be rejuvenating.\n\nWhat are your favorite things to do on a rainy day?",
